Subject: receiving error when running file share report.
Description: i am trying to find folders and files named "HERSHEY" and receiving the following error thousands of times for all folder shares i am scanning: this is an example on one error: error in TraverseDir for "\WWMNYHMIFS01.WWMSYS.COMI$SharesPublicCompanySMRMCommunity ManagementClientsStoliCreativeStaff PhotosTDSalted Karamel?Hershey": The filename, directory name, or volume label syntax is incorrect
Solution_Comment__c:
From the FB folders and files job, I expand the job and expand Configure and click on Query and Query Properties > Configure >
UNC path instead of a drive letter for the Share, and click the three dots on the right to check the connection.
Once we verified the connection, we selected the Share in question and clicked the Add path.
